ered that injury and he needs time to come back and get his feet under the table again, get comfortable and play games.’ ‘Players tend to get long-term injuries and then come back and pick a niggle up somewhere else.’ ‘He will need time to get back into the swing of things.’ Mikel Arteta has his own Brazilian Ronaldo at Arsenal.https://t.co/n7e826J5fk — football.london (@Football_LDN) November 9, 2020 Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world. A pair of one-time Arsenal midfielders have today revealed their admiration for Gabriel Martinelli, as the youngster continues to impress in north London. Arsenal switch 18-year-old attacker Martinelli made the move to the Emirates last summer, from his home country of Brazil. With Arsenal having also secured the high-profile additions… June 14, 2020 In "Sports" Premier League giants Arsenal have this evening confirmed the news that Gabriel Martinelli has put pen-to-paper on a new contract with the club. Arsenal switch Versatile attacker Martinelli only made the move to the Emirates last summer, from his home country of Brazil. With Arsenal having also secured the high-profile… July 3, 2020 In "Sports" As per a report from Spanish outlet Mundo Deportivo, Barcelona have regrets over allowing Gabriel Martinelli to slip through the club’s grasp. Arsenal switch 18-year-old attacker Martinelli made the move to the Emirates this past summer, from his home country of Brazil. With Arsenal having also secured the high-profile additions… November 15, 2019 In "Sports"